title: Planks
info: Planks target your abdominal muscles but give other muscles in your arms.

title: Lunges
info: Lunges strengthen your legs and glutes, stretching the muscles at the same time.

info: Pushups involve multiple muscle groups and are a highly effective strengthening exercise.

title: Overhead dumbbell presses
info: Using two 10-pound dumbbells, this exercise engages muscles in your shoulders, upper back, and core.

title: Single-leg deadlifts
info: Using one 10-pound dumbbell, this exercise improves leg strength and balance.Hold a dumbbell in your right hand

title: Dumbbell rows
info: This exercise uses two 10-pound dumbbells and strengthens multiple upper-body muscles.

title: Side planks
info: Side planks help strengthen your core. Do 3 sets of 10 on each side. Lower your hips back to the floor and repeat.

title: Glute bridge
info: This exercise strengthens your glutes. Hold for a second or two at the top of your lift, then lower your hips back to the floor.

title: Burpees
info: Burpees strengthen multiple muscle groups and also provide a great cardiovascular workout.
